data.description: Welcome to your new home!  Great Southern Lincrest Floor plan.  Enter this home with a formal living room and a formal dining room boasting beautiful hardwoods and heavy molding.  This large living room has a gas log fireplace, hardwood floors, coffered ceilings.  The eat in kitchen features a huge island with bar stool seating, granite countertops, tiled backsplash, pantry, stainless steel appliances and tons of storage.  The kitchen slider takes you to a screened in porch as well as a patio.  The large yard is flat and fenced in.  The downstairs bedroom has a walk in closet and connected bathroom.  Once upstairs bedroom 3 has a ceiling fan and walk in closet.  Bedroom 4 has ceiling fan and walk in closet.  These 2 bedrooms a share a bathroom.  Bedroom 5 has a walk in closet and ceiling fan. Bedroom 6 has a ceiling fan and 2 closets.  Theses bedrooms share a bathroom.  This owner's suite is something to see.  It has a dedicated sitting room, tray ceilings and a walk in closet that has an island in the center.  The owner's suite bathroom has a double vanity, large garden tub, separate shower and a water closet.  This house is something to see.
